  <front>
   <head>A COMPARISON.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="couplet">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">THE lapse of time and rivers is the same,</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Both speed their journey with a restless stream,</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">The silent pace with which they steal away,</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">No wealth can bribe, no pray'rs persuade to stay,</l>
     <l n="5" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Alike irrevocable both when past,</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">And a wide ocean swallows both at last.</l>
     <l n="7" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Though each resemble each in ev'ry part,</l>
     <l n="8" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">A difference strikes at length the musing heart;</l>
     <l n="9" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Streams never flow in vain; where streams abound,</l>
     <l n="10" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">How laughs the land with various plenty crown'd!</l>
     <l n="11" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">But time that should enrich the nobler mind,</l>
     <l n="12" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Neglected, leaves a dreary waste behind.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
